to Pounds 15.6m.
Earnings per share emerged at 2.61p (1.35p) and the final dividend is raised
to 0.8p, making a total of 1.15p (0.8p) for the year.
Interest charges were cut from Pounds 104,000 to Pounds 38,000 and the
company ended the year with zero gearing.
