FT  24 MAY 94 / World News in Brief: Thai tunnel theft
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Thieves in Bangkok made off with 2.5m baht (Dollars 100,000) from a branch
of the Thai Military bank after crawling 2,000 ft along a drainpipe from the
Chao Phraya river and then taking at least a week to dig a 50 ft tunnel into
the bank's vault.
